column3: “First came across this strain when I moved to Colorado the Neighbors love growing anything with chemdawg thus stumbling on to this strain. I was a happy man buying a  half ounce for 65-75 only was a clear steal.”
“Very nice strain, taste like guava and sweet tangerine mixed with diesel/fuel hints.”

“Makes you laugh at yourself while you personify cars and shit. It just makes everything funnier. It's 65% sativa, 35% indica which gives it a great mixture between head and body highs. It's probably my favourite strain to date, would definitely recommend!”
“Got a free seed from Dinachem. Diesel/sweet aroma. Smell was a 10/10. Heavy trich , supplemented room w Co2 (1300ppm) results were outstanding”
“Love it. I feel sooo calm and my body isnt in pain this is worth getting!”
